channel.title: [2006] F2P2006 RS remake Development [2006]
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i779.photobucket.com/albums/yy71/lostmyphat/ftp2006.png[/img]
Ftp2006 is recreating all of the free to play aspects of old runescape. We have most skills, and some quests. Our development thread is here: https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,513804.0.html We are in need of some extra help, as we want quests/other things coming out weekly. (Daniel isn't on this) We expect you to know a fair amount of knowledge from the old runescape days, and java. This project started on [b]9-15-2011[/b], and we have been going hard ever since. You can apply for GfX developer, server developer, client developer, or web developer. [b]You must have Skype. [/b] Format to join: [code]Name: Age: Applying For: Experience: Evidence of previous works: How active will you be: Skype:[/code][/center]
